{
  "stem": "11771.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and I left her there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while we are sitting there, it was already midnight, or more than midnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, the same way it was easy with no problem to get out from the shul through the same window, why I left my brother?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why I left my father when I can say-- I could see other people to do the same thing?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Actually, a few people did it after me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you just say to me, it's a good idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I took myself-- I wasn't lazy-- we're near Radun, by the way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was on the other side of Lithuanian already on the border that was belong officially to White Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there it's a different government, a-- a different order from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they're not working according to rules, according to orders for Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was later, eight months later were the other actions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But meanwhile, eight months is a lot of time in the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people going there, they going to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it's no ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're living free, not like Ejszyszki.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I say, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wasn't lazy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I took the main road about 14 kilometer, about two hours to walk fast.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I go back to Ejszyszki, as I coming in just to Ejszyszki, the Lithuanian catched me, and they start to beat me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They say, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, I'm going to the synagogue where mine whole family is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they beating me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they drag me in, they kick me in in the neighbor synagogue, not in the synagogue from where I left my father with the brother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put me in the old synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
